<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.1">
<l>orunal cuṟṟame ṉakkuyi roṇporuḷ</l>
<l>varunal tolkati yākiya maintaṉai</l>
<l>nerunal kaṇṭatu nīrmalai yiṉṟupōy</l>
<l>karunel cuḻkaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kāṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] dear friend, my life, the man who became</l>
<l>The superior ancient way through which comes great benefit,</l>
<l>Seeing [him] yesterday was in Nīrmalai; going today, we will see [him]</l>
<l>In Kaṇṇamaṅkai, encircled by paddy with kernels.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
